investigation.title: Dose-dependent skeletal deficits due to varied reductions in mechanical loading in rats (Tibia - pQCT)
investigation.description: Reduced skeletal loading leads to marked bone loss. Animal models of hindlimb suspension are widely used to assess alterations in skeleton during the course of complete unloading.
